metadata_completo.sinopse:
Located five stations away from Hokkaido's largest downtown area Susukino. A fun shop called "Snack Busue" can be found run by mama Basue and mama Akemi. Filled with the laughter of the girls and their unusual regulars, you'll be smiling along with them before you know it. 

(Official Site, translated)
